controls.description:
Mechanisms exist to implement Extended Detection & Response (XDR) technologies to correlate data and respond to threats across multiple security layers, including:
(1) Endpoints;
(2) On-premises networks; 
(3) Cloud-based networks;
(4) Electronic communications; 
(5) Applications; and
(6) Services.

